response.original_title: Amos A – en tolkning av en framgångssaga
response.overview: The enigmatic Amos Andersson (1878–1961) is an undisputed dignitary of 20th-century Finnish society. His life can be viewed from the perspectives of many historical developments: support for the arts, queer life, theater, the business world, the press, Finnish-Swedish urban culture, politics.
